{"tid":2103390,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊分享下身邊既熱狗點樣叫人唔好投初選","createTime":"2020-07-11T07:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T14:47:19.000Z","uid":9747,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"252825d45e2121ed4fadb52f6854652bed859d19","tid":2103390,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"「黃屍為投而投，投完唔緊要，後果自己負責啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「投35+既咪又係泛粉」<br />\n「大把唔參加初選既候選人值得支持」<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n今日12點開始投票，同上年區議會選舉樣，可能的話，盡早投票！<br />\n<br />\n記得 WhatsApp 通知屋企人，爸爸媽媽，兄弟姊妹，朋友，同學，同事，鄰居，親戚，今日一齊出黎投票！<br />\n<br />\nAndroid, iPhone 手機都係用網頁投票，投票詳情請大家參考以下網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://landing.popvote.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flanding.popvote.hk%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=6e2c8b39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://landing.popvote.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有，如果大家用左 VPN，請轉番去香港，因為係外國不能投票<br />\n<br />\n如果今日真係冇時間，星期日9點至9點，一樣可以去投票！<br />\n<br />\n初選投票程序如下：<br />\n1⃣登入網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://webapp.popvote.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebapp.popvote.hk&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=fca5c5a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webapp.popvote.hk</a><br />\n2⃣同意個人資料收集聲明<br />\n3⃣輸入4位數字投票點號碼<br />\n投票點地址及號碼： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3fpoHla\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3fpoHla&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=1b2c0c03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3fpoHla</a><br />\n4⃣是否區議會(第二)以外選民？<br />\n5⃣輸入身份證上部分資料<br />\n6⃣選擇候選人<br />\n7⃣產生QR code<br />\n8⃣親身到票站交俾職員核對身份證，住址證明，完成程序<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f18e5c1f764bc1fad5fa01ff5b43a4d474aeaa4","tid":2103390,"uid":9747,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"上街又話送頭<br />\n投票又話無撚用<br />\n究竟熱狗想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1394524d494191efe1f409d50373ed584f99b9a2","tid":2103390,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"由於本土派不承認是次選舉為初選，即使素人全數贏出，亦不代表可以成功爭取2020年立法會議席，假如熱狗輸掉唯一一個議席，更會喪失五區總辭的話語權、另外，本土派認為運動應視為持久抗爭，而不是背水一戰，而選舉中選票亦以投人投黨較多，將投票行為簡化為全民公投難以成立。"},{"pid":"6c010751a3b50beccbe4c0fb526217a9f0adc000","tid":2103390,"uid":9747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1394524d494191efe1f409d50373ed584f99b9a2","tid":2103390,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"由於本土派不承認是次選舉為初選，即使素人全數贏出，亦不代表可以成功爭取2020年立法會議席，假如熱狗輸掉唯一一個議席，更會喪失五區總辭的話語權、另外，本土派認為運動應視為持久抗爭，而不是背水一戰，而選舉中選票亦以投人投黨較多，將投票行為簡化為全民公投難以成立。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"多謝提供例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457c14ec845018759dc05c625faa8711f60a7a59","tid":2103390,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:19:16.000Z","msg":"投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5cba17f1d248e4cbae1081fcf9bb4303e77ee0","tid":2103390,"uid":9747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"得